{"id":604980662,"lang":"python","lang_name":"Python","time":"1 year, 8 months","timestamp":1640092555,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"788 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/604980662/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"3Sum","memory":"16.8 MB","code":"class Solution(object):\n    def threeSum(self, nums):\n        \"\"\"\n        :type nums: List[int]\n        :rtype: List[List[int]]\n        \"\"\"\n        nums.sort()\n        \n        sol = []\n        n = len(nums)\n\n        \n        for i in range(0, n-1):\n            if i != 0 and nums[i] == nums[i-1]:\n                continue\n            k = i+1\n            j = n-1\n            while i < k and k < j:\n                if nums[i] + nums[k] + nums[j] > 0:\n                    j -= 1\n                elif nums[i] + nums[k] + nums[j] < 0:\n                    k += 1\n                else :\n                    sol.append([nums[i], nums[k], nums[j]])\n                    k += 1\n                    while k < j and nums[k] == nums[k-1]:\n                        k += 1\n        \n        return sol","compare_result":"","title_slug":"3sum","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
